                <p class="text-justify">Are you in a hurry because you want to check the flight status for your upcoming trip? Don’t worry about this as well because you need to know about the process for the flight status checking. In this blog, we will share the step-by-step information or process to check <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/major-airlines.aspx"><b>Delta Airlines Flight Status</b></a>. It is the major airline of the United States and with this airline, you can make sure the travel goals in a premium journey manner. Flight status is a useful aspect for the journey through which you can check your flight is on time or delayed. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">1). Visit on www.delta.com: </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">The first step for the passengers is browsing on the Delta Airlines Website and that is www.delta.com. It is the official site of Delta Airlines, where you can do the booking of delta flight as well but flight status can also check directly from the official portal of delta airlines, </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">2). Click on Flight Status in Main Menu: </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">You need to select the option of “Flight Status” in the main menu of the delta airlines home page. Once you select the option then you have to fill in the data to check the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/major-airlines.aspx"><b>Delta Airlines Flights</b></a> status. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">3). Enter Date and Flight Number: </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">At next, you need to enter the date and flight number to precede the flight status check for delta airlines. When you had book the tickets with delta flights then you also received the flight number in the ticket print. </p>
                <h3 class="text-justify">4). Enter Airport Code: </h3>
                <p class="text-justify">At the 4th Step, you need to enter the “From and To” Airport Code”. Once you enter this information then click on the red arrow to continue and the live status will be shown on the page for the flight status and you can check the flight status and leave for the airport according to the flight timing from home. </p>
                <h2 class="text-justify">Check Flight Status on Delta Airlines Mobile Application: </h2>
                <p class="text-justify">The next thing is about the delta airlines mobile application. If you want to check the status of your delta booking easily then you can also download the mobile application of delta airlines on your phone and proceed to check the flight status from the mobile application of delta. In-cast you are not able to find the real or appropriate flight status then you can also get in touch with delta airlines customer services. </p>
